      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure every inch stays spotless. If you're looking for a ride that's practically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Swing by and take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
