      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2001 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This chassis features the S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle body induction. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete: the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates, the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The suspension utilizes OEM-spec dampers and bushings, maintaining the precise turn-in and lateral stability inherent to the M-division's engineering. Paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior exhibits zero bolster wear or pixel degradation on the instrument cluster. A true turnkey example for the technical purist.",
